{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"6069ab19b9","title":"关于修改《矛盾论》给陈伯达、田家英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"67cdbc1141","index":0,"year":1951,"month":3,"day":8,"articleId":"6069ab19b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e46e45351b","name":"陈伯达","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"e58b510cdd","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈伯达，当时任中共中央宣传部副部长。田家英，当时任毛泽东的秘书。他们都参加了《毛泽东选集》的编辑工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c1398b2ac4","type":"title","text":"关于修改《矛盾论》给陈伯达、田家英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"e58b510cdd","type":"paragraph","text":"伯达、家英同志","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"3050d38298","type":"paragraph","text":"《矛盾论》作了一次修改，请即重排清样两份，一份交伯达看，一份送我再看。论形式逻辑的后面几段，词意不畅，还须修改。其他有些部分也还须作小的修改。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"5a89da740d","type":"paragraph","text":"此件在重看之后，觉得以不加入此次选集为宜，因为太象哲学教科书，放入选集将奶碍《实践论》这篇论文的效力，不知你们感觉如何？此点待将来再决定。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"f06d648a7b","type":"paragraph","text":"你们暂时不要来，待《矛盾论》清样再看过及他文看了一部分之后再来，时间大约在月半。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"eec1424b62","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"},{"id":"5f0ecf1c7b","type":"paragraph","text":"三月八日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9"}],"page":{"id":"0a2a15878a","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"6069ab19b9","start":153,"end":153}}}},"__N_SSG":true}